  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the beef and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onion, carrots, and potatoes, cook until the vegetables are tender, about 10 minutes.",
    "Add the horseradish, ferment-kimchi, thyme, salt, and pepper, stir to combine.",
    "Add the vegetable broth and tomato paste, stir to combine, bringing the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, until the stew has thickened, about 20 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
